a user can set up contacts to be notified when a checkpoint is triggered

a user can change active contacts through the GraphQL API

a user can set up checkpoints/alert/agents/triggers/events conditions that are checked on a regular basis

a user can set up actions that are applied when a checkpoint is triggered

an event can be escelated from info/warning/caution/alert levels with an action taken on each

a user can query the API for status information about any checkpoint

a user can subscribe to any checkpoint esclatations through the API

